description: Erection of buildings ranging from 4 to 12-storeys in height to provide 960 sqm of Class A1 (retail) /A2 (financial services) / B1 (office and light industry) / D1 (non residential institutions) or D2 (assembly and leisure) with 123 residential units, comprising 49 x 1 bed, 43 x 2 bed, 21 x 3 bed and 8 x 4 bed and 2 x 8/10 bed units, together with associated car parking and landscaping. Demolition of existing buildings on site.
